{"tid":1265031,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［七一·背水一戰］","createTime":"2019-06-29T03:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T04:58:35.000Z","uid":66130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b30c62e4b5b67dc92629df3a2213e365776dae","tid":1265031,"uid":66130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:49:42.000Z","msg":"相信大家都有睇新聞，林鄭都表明：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不問責下台</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不成立委員會追究警方暴力</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不特赦被捕人士</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且送中都會好大機會下年度立法會再黎<br />\n依幾日搞咁多野警犬都無出手，連胡椒噴霧都唔出<br />\n好明顯上面收到Order<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有邊個可以咁勁令到班狗任鬥任屌唔出手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定係中央，中央唔想香港喺依幾日搞事，令到習種無面。依幾日睇到香港人課金能力好強，全世界都知咩事。<br />\n<br />\n國際輿論既壓力係幫左大家<strong>拖延</strong>，但其實<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無解決到問題！</span><br />\n<br />\n新疆係一個例子，比我地香港面對既問題更嚴重，但無人會出手，點解？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為無利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n香港就唔同，始終國際金融地位高<br />\n但相信G20後，所有野都會捲土重來<br />\n而且會更嚴峻，同五年前一樣，可能仲差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>首先，政府同警察一定會秋後算帳</strong><br />\n遊戲規則一直都喺佢果邊，一兩年後，義士入獄係唔會有人理，好似梁天崎咁，但藍絲同警察就會好願意見你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>然後，無止境抹黑</strong><br />\n行緊街都見到好多人舉撐警banner，我知依班廢佬係無撚用，影響唔到你，但中年丶老一輩丶同警察好buy。隔多一兩個月後，<strong>你又要聽長輩，上司，父母說話</strong><br />\n「班後生又搞事」<br />\n「成班暴徒」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後，繼續溫水煮蛙</strong><br />\n香港人善變，隔一個星期會忘記所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔一年又成班大學生去考警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n議員俾人DQ已經無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以七一要做一件令香港人忘記唔到嘅事<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n大家加油，剩番兩日，諗辦法令更多人企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人...真係好愛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4f389e462ff818da7cde0b09cb14f3aa5fba6d","tid":1265031,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc3722ca94a8c4187f14a9cbd2653345dc4b41f","tid":1265031,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}